---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Early Years Program" lang="en" description="Early Years education for children ages 2-5 at Forest International School Paris">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-[#2d5a3d] to-[#1e3d29] text-white py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="text-[#c9a962] font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Ages 2-5</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mt-2 mb-6">Early Years</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/90">
          Project-based, play, and collaborative exploration to nurture young minds in their most formative years.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Overview -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <span class="text-[#c9a962] font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Program Overview</span>
          <h2 class="section-title mt-2">A Foundation for Lifelong Learning</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            The Early Years education program is for children ages 2 to 5, featuring project-based, play, and collaborative exploration to nurture young minds.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Our early years comprise two sections: <strong>Nursery</strong> (2-4 years old) and <strong>Pre-School</strong> (4-5 years old). Children are divided into two age groups so they feel supported as they grow.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Students may attend for either half or full days, and a minimum of three half days is recommended so they fully benefit from the programmes.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#4a7c5c] to-[#2d5a3d] rounded-2xl p-8 text-white">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Program Details</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#c9a962] mr-3 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Nursery:</strong> 2-4 years old</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#c9a962] mr-3 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Pre-School:</strong> 4-5 years old</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#c9a962] mr-3 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Class Size:</strong> Maximum 5 students (younger) / 11 (older)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#c9a962] mr-3 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span><strong>French:</strong> 4.5 hours per week</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#c9a962] mr-3 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Fees:</strong> 19,500 - 23,500 EUR/year</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Curriculum -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="text-[#c9a962] font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Learning</span>
        <h2 class="section-title mt-2">Our Curriculum</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 text-center">
          The Early Years curriculum is lively, building on what each child already knows and opening up exciting new ways to learn.
        </p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#2d5a3d] mb-3">Specialist Teachers</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">In addition to the class teacher, children enjoy visits from specialist teachers for Music, Sport, and French lessons.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#2d5a3d] mb-3">Language Learning</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Language acquisition focuses on fun, discovery, and communication with 4.5 hours of immersive French sessions each week.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#2d5a3d] mb-3">School Activities</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Even the youngest children join in with assemblies, themed days, and school trips, designed to make their transition through the school easier.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#2d5a3d] mb-3">Nature Exploration</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Daily forest activities where children learn through exploration and discovery, making learning a fun and exciting journey.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-[#f0f7f2]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="section-title">Give Your Child the Best Start</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-8">
        Contact us to learn more about our Early Years program and schedule a visit.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/en/admissions" class="btn-primary">Apply Now</a>
        <a href="/en/contact" class="btn-secondary">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
